``a tribute to our doctors ... and to the good care afforded to my
husband and me during the past several years at Presbyterian
Hospital.''
   Fogelson, a Texas oilman, died at Presbyterian Hospital in
December.
   Mrs. Fogelson recently endowed a chair in her husband's memory
at the University of Texas Southwestern Medical Center in Dallas.
